OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy start with some patchy
OL,6,Frain in the west. Otherwise mainly dry
OL,7,Fwith some bright spells breaking
OL,8,Fthrough by afternoon, these mainly
OL,9,Facross the east. Western Isles staying
OL,10,Fcloudy with the odd light shower.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FMainly dry this evening and
OL,13,Fovernight, the odd shower in the
OL,14,Fnorthwest. Persistent rain will spread
OL,15,Finto the northwest later in the night.
OL,16,FClear spells in the east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
