OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FCloudy with rain spreading
OL,6,Fsoutheast across all parts, lingering
OL,7,Finto the afternoon in the east.
OL,8,FTurning drier in the north and west
OL,9,Fthrough the afternoon. A colder day.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FDry
OL,12,Ffor most of Thursday but rain
OL,13,Fspreading east later. Unsettled with
OL,14,Fshowers or longer spells of rain on
OL,15,FFriday and Saturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
